      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">High angle indoor panorama shot of a group of men: At the centre of the picture a man is seated on a chair decorated with crowns in front of a full length portrait painting. He is wearing a military uniform adorned with many insignias of honour and a fur cap displaying a coat of arms. The man is reading from a sheet of paper. There are 15 men standing on the steps to his left and to his right. Some of them are wearing official military uniforms and are holding their hats with cockades in their hands. Two are in Orthodox priests' vestments and some others are wearing plain city clothes. Most of the men are adorned with insignia of honour.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The Bulgarian Prince Ferdinand reading his King's speech in Parliament in front of Konstantin Stoilov's government and deputies.</ab>
